---
title: CRM Revenue Lifecycle — Pipeline Flow Diagram
---
flowchart TD
    A([Lead Identified\n5%]) --> B([Qualification\n15%])
    B --> C([Discovery and Assessment\n30%])
    C --> D([Solution Design\n50%])
    D --> E([Proposal Submitted\n65%])
    E --> F([Negotiation\n80%])
    F --> G([Contract Pending Signature\n90%])
    G --> H{Decision}
    H -->|Won| I([Closed Won\n100%])
    H -->|Lost| J([Closed Lost\n0%])

    I -->|Automation Trigger| K([Contract Initiated])
    K --> L([Asset Inventory Phase])
    L --> M([Vendor Alignment Phase])
    M --> N([Service Deployment])
    N --> O([Active Operations])
    O -->|90 days before end| P{Renewal?}
    P -->|Yes| Q([Contract Renewed])
    P -->|No| R([Contract Terminated])

    O --> S([Service Request Logged])
    S --> T([Technician Assigned])
    T --> U([Service In Progress])
    U --> V([Repair Completed])
    V --> W([Validation Completed])
    W --> X([Event Closed])

    X -->|Billable check| Y([Invoice Generated])
    Y --> Z([Invoice Delivered])
    Z --> AA([Payment Pending])
    AA -->|Paid| AB([Payment Received])
    AA -->|Overdue| AC([Overdue])
    AC --> AD([Collections])

    AB -->|With cost records| AE([Margin Calculated])

    style I fill:#22c55e,color:#fff
    style J fill:#ef4444,color:#fff
    style O fill:#3b82f6,color:#fff
    style AB fill:#22c55e,color:#fff
    style AE fill:#8b5cf6,color:#fff
    style AC fill:#f59e0b,color:#fff
    style AD fill:#ef4444,color:#fff
    style Q fill:#22c55e,color:#fff
    style R fill:#ef4444,color:#fff
